{"tid":1591498,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［和你塞效應］香港航空高層本月起減薪兩成 勸員工下月放最少2日無薪假","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T15:34:51.000Z","uid":34154,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cd9a47456fc9bf2a2fc098d7541313446cb844","tid":1591498,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"香港航空今日向員工發內部電郵，指為進一步減省營運開支，公司高級管理層已同意9月起減薪兩成，為期4個月；同時呼籲員工參與公司推出的無薪假計劃（No Pay Leave Scheme)。<br />\n<br />\n本報獲得港航人力資源部及行政部的內部電郵，電郵中表示，面對當時旅遊需求相當疲弱，公司已作出一系列減省成本的措施，包括減少運力及航班班次、暫停一切非必要工作項目及招聘等，但仍難以抵銷營運航空公司的巨大開支。為進一步降低人力成本，高級管理層已同意由今年9月起至12月，下調薪金20%。<br />\n<br />\n公司又呼籲香港及內地的地勤員工，參與無薪假計劃，建議助理經理或以下職級員工每月放最少2日無薪假，經理級或以上每月放4日，又歡迎員工可申報多於公司建議的日數。計劃暫定由10月開始，為期3個月。公司將會就機艙服務員推出另一計劃，但電郵中未有提及另一計劃的具體細節。<br />\n<br />\n本報正就新計劃向香港航空查詢。<br />\n<br />\n記者：邱曉欣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190924/60079432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60079432&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqBlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=351612be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60079432&h=abeb58ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190924/60079432</a><br />\n<br />\n和你塞真心有成效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e51e90d3ac9ede4a34c00d33906624295d9a7e","tid":1591498,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06e994c559c5f790b762b